These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, september, december, january
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, spanish, polish
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, black, blood-red
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, lily, zinnia
City: hannover, edinburgh, london, venice
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bongani, vegafina, pall-mall
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, mouse, bird
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the indonesian##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the owner of the frog is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
11. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in september##1
12. the owner of the turtle is the person traveling to london##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
14. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in january##1
15. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who likes black##1
16. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
17. the person who's birthday is in december is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Birthday      | october       | january      | december       | september    |
| Nationality         | indonesian    | polish    | nigerian      | spanish    |
| Color           | blood-red | azure       | black | mauve     |
| Flower   | amaryllis         | lily  | zinnia      | sunflower     |
| City   | edinburgh          | venice     | london       | hannover |
| Cigar         | vegafina       | bongani | pall-mall       | montecristo   |
| Pet     | bird     | mouse  | turtle         | frog   |

