4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, havana, siglo, bongani
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, bartender, software-developer, dressmaker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, soccer, skateboarding, rowing
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, chess, backgammon
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the bartender is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the police-officer is on the left of the dressmaker##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the dressmaker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
13. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
14. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
15. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
16. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
17. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| City          | miami     | boston     | venice      | marseilles  |
| Flower         | daisy  | aconite  | zinnia      | tulip |
