4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, cain, vegafina, bolivar
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, marigold, daisy
House: farmhouse, cottage, art-deco, colonial
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, ship, van
City: rome, san-francisco, new-york, nizza
 1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the italian##1
 2. the italian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the farmhouse house is the italian##1
 4. the russian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the cottage house is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the van is the person who growsrose##1
11. the cain-smoker is the russian##1
12. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the van##1
13. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
14. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
15. the person who's birthday is in july is the colonial house##1
16. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
17. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |     3     |      4      |
| Nationality          | spanish          | indonesian        | italian      | russian      |
